  "title": "Audit Executive ( External / Audit Firm )  - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Audit Associate</strong></p><p><strong>5 days / 5.5 days(Saturday half day during peak period)</strong><br />0830am - 1730pm<br />Up to $3500<br />Beach Road</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Undertakes specific stages of audit work under supervision.</li><li>Appreciate the underlying principles behind the tasks assigned as part of the audit plan.</li><li>Able to make adjustments to the application of skills to improve the work tasks or solve non-complex issues.</li><li><em><strong>Able to build relationships, work in a team and identify ethical issues with reference to the code of professional conduct and ethics.</strong></em></li><li>Select and apply from a range of known solutions to familiar problems and takes responsibility for own learning and performance.</li><li>Work with any of the assurance teams to obtain an understanding of our client’s business.</li><li>Develop an audit plan/strategy for an audit of financial statements and document the planning procedures.</li><li>Prepare/tailor audit programmes based on areas of audit emphasis determined at the planning stage.</li><li>Perform audit tests of controls and substantive procedures based on planned audit approach to address the various assertions, eg: existence & completeness, rights and obligations, valuation, accuracy, presentation and disclosure.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree or equivalent</li><li>1-2 year of working experience as audit associate.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, WA your resume to ‪‪+65 9136 9792‬‬ or email your resume to supreme.yentan@gmail.com.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>TAN YEN ZHEN (CHEN YANZHEN) REG NO: R25138932</p><p>THE SUPREMEHR ADVISORY PTE LTD EA NO: 14C7279</p>",
